snippet.title: ChamferZone
snippet.description:
Hi! 👋🙂I'm Tim - Sr. 3D Artist with 14 years of industry experience having worked at Crytek, Ubisoft and Digital Extremes and my own boss at ChamferZone Inc. In my tutorials I'll show you every step in creating AAA quality 3D Game Art to get you industry ready too! This is my mission and commitment to you 💪🤝

• https://discord.gg/s98PbNk7pM -  Come and join our awesome 3D Art community! 
• https://www.artstation.com/artist/timbergholz - Here you can see all my work
• https://www.youtube.com/c/chamferzone - Watch free tutorials 
• https://twitter.com/ChamferZone - I am not that active on twitter but good place for announcements
• https://www.facebook.com/ChamferZone - same here ;)
